EAIF invested XOF15 billion in a bond issue that raised XOF100 billion (ca. US$170 million) for investment in the Senegal business of Sonatel S.A, a West African telecommunications company. Sonatel will use the bond proceeds to extend and enlarge its 4G + network in urban and rural areas and renew and upgrade service platforms. Sonatel is investing in new activities such as energy, banking and multimedia content, which will benefit from the bond fundraising.
